notes.title: Copypasta
notes.content: London's current population is estimated at 9,304,016. To figure out the length of the conga line, I first looked up the average shoe size in the UK. The male average is a size 8, female is a size 6, which are 26cm and 25.1cm, respectively. London is 52% female and 48% male, so that's 4,838,088 women and 4,465,928 men (not taking into account any nonbinary folks who might also live in London and wear shoes.) For simplicity's sake, let's assume that every citizen of London is able to stand in a conga line, they all wear the average shoe size for their gender, and they're all standing with the toes of their shoes touching the heels of the person in front of them. 4,838,088 women x 25.1cm = 121,436,008.8cm = 1214.36km 4,465,928 men x 26cm = 116,114,128cm = 1161.14km So the conga line is 2375.5 km long. Let's find out how long it would take to run it! Extreme long distance runner Dean Karnazes is known for running 350 miles (563.27km) in 80 hours and 44 minutes without stopping, making his average speed 6.98km/hr. Let's assume that Miley and the people of London have been training their whole lives in preparation for this event, so they will be able to continuously run at Karnazes's average speed of 6.98km/hr until Miley has run past everyone. Since they're running in opposite directions, they'll be passing each other at a speed of 13.96km/hr. For Miley to cross paths with every single person in the line, it would take just over 170 hours and 14 minutes of nonstop running, at which point everyone involved will have most likely died from exhaustion. TL;DR - No, it would not be possible for Miley Cyrus to meet everyone in London in one day.

notes.content: It seems that there are some misconceptions with my LIMITED EDITION Fanta yo-yo so I just want to clear a few things up. Firstly the LIMITED EDITION Fanta yo-yo IS NOT for sale! I would like to specify that the LIMITED EDITION Fanta yo-yo is PRICELESS and every time I yo the yo it loses 100 million entire dollars of worth. This would only be an issue if my LIMITED EDITION Fanta yo-yo wasn't fucking PRICELESS. Last thing before I go is that when I die I will have my LIMITED EDITION Fanta yo-yo burned and have its ashes scattered into space so that it is impossible for it to come back. My LIMITED EDITION Fanta yo-yo shall never be fabricated by the likes of any other mortal and if those dare to attempt then you will be hunted down by my LIMITED EDITION Fanta private corporation. That is all.
